item.title: Rouge Double Intensite
item.dc:creator: brian
item.description:
A lip duo. On one side, a long-wear "liquid" lipstick. On the other, a shiny and comfortable gloss.
Result: intense, shiny and ultra-long wear makeup.

item.title: Rouge Coco Stylo
item.dc:creator: brian
item.description: ROUGE COCO STYLO. A lipstick pen that lets your lips flaunt a style and make a statement in a single step. A travel-friendly lipstick that goes wherever you do. With its hybrid formula, as intense as a lipstick, as shiny as a gloss and as comfortable as a balm, ROUGE COCO STYLO inaugurates a new chapter in makeup.

item.title: Rouge Allure Gloss
item.dc:creator: brian
item.description: An exceptional gloss to wear like a lipstick. The first gloss that combines lacquered shine with the bold style of an intense colour. A click and a black case that are now part of the ROUGE ALLURE legend. A gloss for women who love lipstick. A lipstick for women who love gloss.

item.title: Rouge Coco Shine
item.dc:creator: brian
item.description:
A lipstick with a melt-away balm texture that becomes fluid as soon as it touches the lips. A palette of dazzling shades, from semi-sheer to more intense. The lightweight, shiny version of ROUGE COCO, contained in a travel-friendly and practical metal tube faithful to the black and gold codes of the House.
Result: a wet effect with natural shine.

item.title: Lvres Scintillantes
item.dc:creator: brian
item.description:
An ultra-shiny gloss, an endless palette of shades and effects. Easy and quick application. A creamy, non-sticky gel that moisturises and shapes the lips in an instant.
Result: ultra-shiny, fresh and sparkling makeup.

item.title: Rouge Allure
item.dc:creator: brian
item.description:
A vibrant and luminous lipstick. An ultra-fine, melt-away and second-skin texture, a palette of intense shades. A bold and daring style.
Result: deep, radiant and satiny makeup. Perfect wear from the very first stroke.

item.title: Rouge Allure Ink
item.dc:creator: brian
item.description: ROUGE ALLURE INK. A matte liquid lip colour. An intense and luminous ink. With its fine and dense pigments, it instantly and weightlessly fuses with the lips for a long-lasting result (8 hrs*). The daring allure that never goes unnoticed.

item.title: Dior Addict Lip Maximizer
item.dc:creator: brian
item.description: The first instant-volume gloss from Dior Backstage. Dior Addict Lip Maximizer moisturizes lips and gives an incredible instant-volume effect for a glossy smile and full, plump lips, as if transformed. Its mint-vanilla scent provides an even more addictive fresh sensation.
item.content:encoded:
The first instant-volume gloss from Dior Backstage.
Dior Addict Lip Maximizer moisturizes lips and gives an incredible instant-volume effect for a glossy smile and full, plump lips, as if transformed. Its mint-vanilla scent provides an even more addictive fresh sensation.
